<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Pass the Bread Basket</title>
    <link href="/global_styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <section>
        <h1>Pass the Bread Basket</h1>
        <!-- <h2>Handling those extra slices</h2> -->
        <h2>Feed your cooking addiction and Neighbors</h2>
        <p>Fuel your baking or cooking addiction and get acquainted with your neighbors at the same time through Pass the Bread Basket. An app that allows neighbors in your building to call dibs on a serving of a homemade good.</p>
        <button class="button--default"><a href="/buildings/">Find Your Building</a></button>
        <button class="button--accent">View Selected Servings</button>
    </section>
    <section>
        <div>
            <!-- <h3>Make something</h3> -->
            <h3>Make a thing</h3>
            <p>Cook or bake a recipe</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3>Add it</h3>
            <p>Take a picture of the item and add it to your buildings “Available Food” Page</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3>Wait</h3>
            <p>Wait for people to select servings and for the specific time slot selected to arrive</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3>Pass it out</h3>
            <p> Give it to your neighbors when they arrive</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>